extends _layouts/template

block head
  link(rel="stylesheet", href="/css/generic.css")

block content
  .about-container
    header.about-header
      h1.about-title About The Shed Place
      p.about-subtitle Serving Hohenwald and surrounding communities with quality outdoor structures and more since 2019

    .about-grid
      .about-image-container
        img.about-image(
          src="/assets/logos/light.svg",
          alt="The Shed Place storefront"
        )
      .about-content
        h2.about-section-title Our Story
        p.about-text
          | Welcome to The Shed Place! We are a family-owned and operated business
          | proudly serving Hohenwald and the surrounding communities since 2019.
          | As a dedicated family of six, we juggle the responsibilities of running
          | two businesses, homeschooling our four children, and homesteading our
          | off-grid home.

        p.about-text
          | Our core values of honesty, trust, and integrity are at the heart of
          | everything we do. We believe in treating our customers with the same
          | respect and care that we would want to be treated with. This commitment
          | to exceptional service and quality workmanship sets us apart and ensures
          | a positive experience for all our clients.

    .about-values
      .about-value-card
        h3.about-value-title Honesty
        p.about-value-text
          | We believe in transparent communication and always being truthful
          | with our customers about their options and expectations.

      .about-value-card
        h3.about-value-title Trust
        p.about-value-text
          | Building lasting relationships with our customers through
          | reliability and consistent quality service.

      .about-value-card
        h3.about-value-title Integrity
        p.about-value-text
          | Making decisions based on what's right, not what's easy,
          | and standing behind our work and products.

      .about-value-card
        h3.about-value-title Family Values
        p.about-value-text
          | Running our business with the same care and attention
          | we give to our own family.

    .about-cta
      p.about-text.mb-6
        | Thank you for choosing The Shed Place. We look forward to serving you
        | and helping you bring your visions to life.
      a.about-button(href="/contact") Contact Us Today
